OL,3,CBus drivers call for 'Bill of Rights'
OL,4,Cto make working conditions safer
OL,6,FBus drivers are calling on Transport
OL,7,Ffor London and bus companies to
OL,8,Fintroduce a series of protections in
OL,9,Ftheir contracts that they say would
OL,10,Fhelp make their jobs safer and improve
OL,11,Fthe way they work.
OL,13,FITV News London has previously spoken
OL,14,Fwith drivers who said they have to
OL,15,Fendure long hours in hot and often
OL,16,Fdirty conditions.
OL,18,FNow London Assembly members have
OL,19,Fagreed a motion for a 'Bill of Rights'
OL,20,Fthat would see contractual protections
OL,21,Ffor drivers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
