CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783689573
OL,3,CBus drivers call for 'Bill of Rights'
OL,4,Cto make working conditions safer
OL,6,FThe rights would include:
OL,8,FHaving been agreed by the Assembly,
OL,9,Fthe motion will now be put forward to
OL,10,Fthe Mayor, who will now have to
OL,11,Fformally respond.
OL,13,FMembers want Sir Sadiq Khan to back
OL,14,Fthe Bus Drivers' Bill of Rights and
OL,15,Fwork with operators and unions to
OL,16,Fensure conditions improve for drivers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783689573
OL,3,CBus drivers call for 'Bill of Rights'
OL,4,Cto make working conditions safer
OL,6,FReform UK's Keith Prince , who
OL,7,Fproposed the motion, said: "I am
OL,8,Fimmensely pleased that the Assembly
OL,9,Fhas agreed that the welfare, dignity
OL,10,Fand safety of London's bus drivers
OL,11,Fshould be a priority for the Mayor and
OL,12,FTfL.
OL,14,F"Drivers and their trade unions have
OL,15,Fbeen raising concerns for a long time,
OL,16,Fand those concerns have now been
OL,17,Fformally recognised."
OL,19,FFormer London bus driver Kevin Mustafa
OL,20,Fhas been a leading force in the
OL,21,Fcampaign for bus driver rights.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783689573
OL,3,CBus drivers call for 'Bill of Rights'
OL,4,Cto make working conditions safer
OL,6,FHe told ITV News London the "system
OL,7,Fhas been broken" for years.
OL,9,F"Every time you raise it with the
OL,10,Fpeople that are in power, like the
OL,11,FMayor of London or Transport for
OL,12,FLondon, they seem to turn a blind eye
OL,13,Fand they don't listen to what we're
OL,14,Ftelling them.
OL,16,F"Bus drivers in London have been
OL,17,Freporting issues for the last 10 years
OL,18,Feven ... There's too many accidents on
OL,19,Fthe road, there's too many drivers
OL,20,Ffalling asleep at the wheel.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783689573
OL,3,CBus drivers call for 'Bill of Rights'
OL,4,Cto make working conditions safer
OL,6,F"There's too many drivers overheating
OL,7,Fin cabs. There's too much danger out
OL,8,Fthere for bus drivers that puts public
OL,9,Fat risk."
OL,11,FLorna Murphy, TfL's Director of Buses,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Bus drivers play an essential
OL,13,Frole in keeping the capital moving.
OL,15,F"Alongside bus operators, we take
OL,16,Ftheir safety and welfare seriously and
OL,17,Fwe rightly require operators to meet
OL,18,Fhigh standards.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783689573
OL,3,CBus drivers call for 'Bill of Rights'
OL,4,Cto make working conditions safer
OL,6,F"We are working together on a range of
OL,7,Fmeasures to further improve working
OL,8,Fconditions, health and wellbeing.
OL,10,F"We are committed to ensuring that all
OL,11,Fstaff have a fair work schedule, with
OL,12,Fsafe vehicles and access to the
OL,13,Ffacilities they need to carry out
OL,14,Ftheir roles effectively. We regularly
OL,15,Fengage with Unite the Union on these
OL,16,Fmatters."
OL,18,FShe went on to say that reports from
OL,19,Fdrivers are "always fully
OL,20,Finvestigated".
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783689573
OL,3,CBus drivers call for 'Bill of Rights'
OL,4,Cto make working conditions safer
OL,6,F"Our operators should never take
OL,7,Faction against people raising concerns
OL,8,Fabout welfare.
OL,10,F"We value all feedback from the
OL,11,Fthousands of people who work
OL,12,Ftirelessly to keep London's bus
OL,13,Fnetwork moving and would encourage
OL,14,Fanyone experiencing issues to raise
OL,15,Fthese with their employer, their union
OL,16,For the Confidential Incident Reporting
OL,17,F& Analysis Service anonymously."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
